---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Add-On Services – Bliss Dermacare" description="Enhance your skincare experience with our premium add-on services. LED light therapy, advanced treatments, and more to complement any facial.">

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-[#faf9f7] border-b border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-4 block">Enhance Your Experience</span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif text-neutral-900 mb-4">Add-On Services</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600">Elevate any treatment with our curated selection of premium add-ons designed to maximize results and extend benefits.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Add-Ons Grid -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="mb-10">
        <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-3 block">Boosters & Enhancements</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-neutral-900">Perfect Your Results</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-2">Add these services to any appointment for deeper penetration, longer-lasting benefits, and visible transformation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- LED Light Therapy Add-On -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-48 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-300 to-primary-500">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-24 h-24 text-white opacity-20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707M16 12a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">LED Light Therapy</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Non-invasive light technology to boost collagen production, reduce inflammation, and accelerate skin healing.</p>
            <div class="mb-5">
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-2"><span class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Add to any facial:</span> +$35</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-600 font-medium">Extends treatment time by 15 minutes</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-7 text-sm text-neutral-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Boosts collagen & elasticity
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Reduces redness & inflammation
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Accelerates skin healing
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Pain-free, no downtime
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/book/" class="block text-center bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors text-sm font-medium">Add to Booking</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- High Frequency Skin Tightening -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-48 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-300 to-blue-500">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-24 h-24 text-white opacity-20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">High Frequency Skin Tightening</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Advanced thermal energy technology to stimulate collagen and visibly lift, firm, and contour the complexion.</p>
            <div class="mb-5">
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-2"><span class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">30-minute treatment:</span> $250 (Groupon: $45)</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-600 font-medium">Pairs perfectly with facials</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-7 text-sm text-neutral-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Stimulates natural collagen
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Visibly lifts & firms skin
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Improves skin texture
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Results visible after first session
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/book/" class="block text-center bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors text-sm font-medium">Add to Booking</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Brazilian/Bikini Waxing -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-48 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-300 to-amber-500">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-24 h-24 text-white opacity-20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Brazilian/Bikini Waxing</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Professional waxing with high-quality, gentle waxes for smooth, flawless results with minimized discomfort.</p>
            <div class="mb-5">
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-2"><span class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Single session:</span> $45 (Groupon: $20)</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-600 font-medium">Results last 3-4 weeks</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-7 text-sm text-neutral-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Long-lasting smooth skin
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Expert technique minimizes discomfort
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Progressively easier with repeat visits
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Packages available for savings
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/book/" class="block text-center bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors text-sm font-medium">Add to Booking</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Eye & Brow Services Section -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-neutral-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="mb-10">
        <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-3 block">Eyes & Brows</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-neutral-900">Lash & Brow Enhancement</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-2">Defined, beautiful lashes and brows that frame your face and enhance natural beauty with our specialized services.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Lash Lift & Brow Lamination -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-300 to-pink-500">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-24 h-24 text-white opacity-20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Lash Lift & Brow Lamination</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Semi-permanent curl for lashes paired with full, feathered, and perfectly groomed brows that stay in place.</p>
            <div class="mb-5">
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-2"><span class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Treatment:</span> $72 (Groupon: $36)</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-600 font-medium">Lasts 6-8 weeks</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-7 text-sm text-neutral-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Low-maintenance for daily wear
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                No curling iron needed
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Natural, polished look
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Perfect complement to any facial
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/book/" class="block text-center bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors text-sm font-medium">Add to Booking</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Lash Extensions -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-primary-100 hover:border-primary-300">
          <div class="relative h-52 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-300 to-purple-500">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-24 h-24 text-white opacity-20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Eyelash Extensions</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm mb-4">Customizable lash extensions from subtle enhancement to bold, high-impact drama in multiple styles and volumes.</p>
            <div class="mb-5">
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-2"><span class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Full Set + Fill:</span> $72 (Groupon: $36)</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-600 font-medium">Lasts 4-6 weeks, fills every 2-3 weeks</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 mb-7 text-sm text-neutral-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Choose from Classic, Hybrid, Volume, Mega Volume
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Customized to your eye shape
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                No mascara needed
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Wakes up with glamorous lashes
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/book/" class="block text-center bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors text-sm font-medium">Add to Booking</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Add-Ons Section -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="text-primary-600 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-semibold mb-3 block">The Science</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-neutral-900">Why Combine Services?</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Amplified Results</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Layering complementary treatments creates synergistic effects that enhance each other for more dramatic, visible outcomes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m7 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Extended Benefits</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Add-ons extend the duration of results and maintain improvements longer between regular maintenance appointments.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Complete Transformation</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-600">Address multiple skin concerns in one visit for a comprehensive beauty upgrade that transforms your entire appearance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-14 bg-neutral-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif mb-4">Ready to Upgrade Your Experience?</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 text-lg mb-8">Our skincare specialists can recommend the perfect add-ons for your goals during your consultation.</p>
      <a href="/book/" class="inline-block bg-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-semibold">Book Your Appointment</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
